summary:
Results-oriented, entrepreneur, the ultimate “get it done” individual. Nathaly has hands-on experience as a Digital Strategist and Product Leader for Europe, Latam, and USA for large complex organizations and fast-growing startups/scaleups. 

Her customer-centric approach, data-driven mindset, and marketing + UX background make her a trusted leader who accelerates growth and product innovation. She transitioned successfully across industries, from finance to the e-commerce sector and from non-profit to B-corp organizations. 


Visit my website: https://inti.digital/
Say Hi: hello@inti.digital

Their mission is to build an empowered community of local professionals who contribute to a more sustainable society through their careers. 

The primary business needs:
 Increase Membership Numbers
Keep current Net Impact community engaged 

After UX research, our insight:
The user doesn’t know how to set up the path for moving his career into his “green dream job.” We want to be guided/oriented for more experienced professionals who have already been through the same. It’s crucial for the user that these professionals share the same values and passion for sustainability.

Solution:
We redesign the Net Impact website, adding a career section and mentorship program. 

Role:
From ideation to implementation bringing this project to life together with the developer and content team.
